<br>
Gray and I met on the Butcherblock docks, and there began our long habit of dicing when we met. The wagers were quite innocent despite certain suggestions to the contrary. I often had to however extricate young rangers and such from his clutches as he cast his spells upon them. Truly the evil twin of Blayze...<br>
<br>
Our first large event with the League of Shadows was held I think in Lower Guk, where we outdrank even their mightiest troll  (*blushingly confesses to winning the bout with Mudwart?). Many other duels, arena challenges and battles have followed. The rivalry is much fun, to this day I count you as my favourite enemies.<br>
