That's right, Katinka was kidnapped back to Neriak by the Duke she had been promised to by her house, Gray never got to marry her.  Valdria he married in Mistmoore Castle, with Thrads performing the ceremony, and then Syllestrae in a quiet ceremony in the Tower of Frozen Shadows sometime thereafter.  Lynnette had fallen into her coma by that point and vanished, so they didn't actually marry.  By the time Lynnette recovered, Valdria had vanished while in search of their kidnapped child, and Sumida claimed Gray for her own (and that's one ranger that Meledi failed to 'rescue').<br>
